quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  7,65,"Aadfoͻ nso wͻn nua Huud kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, (efrisε) monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Enti monnnsuro Nyankopͻn na monnyε ahwεyie?”"
  7,66,"Nhemfo {anaa mpanimfoͻ} boniayεfoͻ a εwͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Nokorε, yehu wo sε wo wͻ agyimisεm mu na yε’dwen sε woka nkontompofoͻ no ho"
  7,67,"Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, εnyε gyimii na m’agyimi, na mmom meyε Ɔsomafoͻ fri Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ “"
  7,68,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro na merebɔ akyerε mo, na meyε ofutufo pa nokwafoͻ ma mo"
  7,69,"Anaasε εyε mo nwanwa sε Afutusεm fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ nam mo mu nipa bi so aba mo hͻ sε ͻmεbͻ mo kͻkͻ? Monkae εberε a Ɔyεε mo ananmusifoͻ wͻ Noa nkorͻfoͻ no akyi, na Ɔmaa mo nkͻsoͻ wͻ abͻdeε (a atwa moho ahyia) no mu. Enti monkae Nyankopͻn adom, sεdeε mobedi nkonim"
  7,70,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Wobaa yεn hͻ sεdeε yεbεsom Nyankopͻn nko ara, na yεbegyae deε na y’agyanom som? Ɛneε fa deε worehyε yεn ho bͻ no bra, sε woka nokwafoͻ no ho ampa a”"
  7,71,"Ɔkaa sε: “Nokorε asotwee ne abufuo fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba mo so. Moregye me akyinnye wͻ (abosom) din a mo ne moagya nom atotoͻ no ho, abrɛ a Nyankopͻn nsianee tumi biara wɔ ho? Eneɛ montwεn, na meka mo ne wͻn a wͻ’retwεn no ho"
  7,72,Enti Yε’de ahummͻborͻ a efiri Yεn hͻ no gyee no ne wͻn a wͻ’ka ne ho no nkwa. Na Yε’tͻree wͻn a wͻ’faa Yεn Nsεm no atorͻsεm no ase. Na (saa nkorͻfoͻ no) nyε agyidiefoͻ
  7,73,"Samuudfoͻ no nso (Yε’somaa) wͻn nua Soalih maa no kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, na monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Ampa sε (Nokorε) pefee fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba mo hͻ; woi yε Nyankopͻn yoma bedeε a ͻyε nsεnkyerεnee ma mo; enti monyae no ma no nidi wͻ Nyankopͻn asaase no so, na monhwε na moanyε no bͻne, anyε saa a asotwee a εyε ya paa bεsͻ mo mu"
  7,74,"Monkae εberε a Ɔyεε mo ananmusifoͻ wͻ Aadfoͻ no akyi, de mo tenaa asaase no soͻ, na mosisii mo abansoroͻ wͻ ne petee no mu, san bͻne mmepͻ mu yεε no adan. Enti monkae Nyankopͻn adom, na monhwε yie na moanni nsεmͻnee wͻ asaase no so"
  7,75,"Nhemfo (anaa mpanimfoͻ) a wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ wͻ ne nkorͻfoͻ no mu no ka kyerεε wͻn a wͻ’yε mmrε na wͻ’agye adi wͻ wͻn mu no sε: “Monim sε Soalh yε obia ne Wura Nyankopͻn na asoma no? “Wͻ’kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yε’gye deε yεde asoma no no di”"
  7,76,"Wͻn a wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yε’deε, yεnnye deε mogye die no nni “"
  7,77,"Enti wͻ’kum yoma bedeε no, na wͻ’tee wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε no so atua, kaa sε: “Soalh, fa deε w’ahyε yεn ho bͻ no bra, sε woka (Nyame) asomafoͻ no ho ampa a”"
  7,78,"Enti asaase wosoͻ sͻͻ wͻn mu, na wͻ’yεε dinn wͻ wͻn afie mu"
  7,79,"Enti (Soalh) danee ne ho fri wͻn ho kaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, mebͻͻ mo me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro kyerεε mo, na metuu mo fo, nanso moampε afotuo no”"
  7,80,"Ɛna Lut nso, εberε a ͻka kyerεε ne nkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Mobͻ ahohwi bra a amansan no mu biara nnii moanim kan nyεε bi da?”"
  7,81,"“Nokorε sε, mofri mmaa akyi de akͻnnͻ kͻ mmarima ho. Daabi, moyε nnipa a modi nsεmᴐne.”"
  7,82,"Ne nkorͻfoͻ no mmuaeε a wͻ’de maeε ara nesε: “Montu wͻn mfri mo kuro no mu; efrisε, wͻ’yε nipa a wͻ’pε ahoteε“"
  7,83,"Enti Yε’gyee ͻne n’abusuafoͻ nkwa, gyesε neyere, na ͻka wͻn a wͻ’kaa akyire no ho"
  7,84,Na Yε’tͻͻ nsuo paa gu wͻn so. Enti hwε sεdeε abͻneεfoͻ no awieε si wieε
  7,85,"Ɛna Mad’yan nso wͻn nua Shua’ib kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Ampa, nyinasoͻ pefee fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba mo hͻ; enti (sε morehyε adeε ama obi a) monhyε ma εnyε ma, na monsusu (biribiara nso pεpεεpε) na monhwε na moanfa nyansa kwan ante amanfoͻ nneεma so, afei εmma monni nsεmͻne wͻ asaase no so wͻ akyire yi a yatoto biribiara wͻ so pεpεεpε. Saa na εyε papa ma mo sε moyε gyidiefoͻ ampa a"
  7,86,"Monhwε na moantenatena akwan biara so anhunahuna wͻn, annsi wͻn a wͻ’agye adie no kwan amfri Nyankopͻn kwan no so anhwehwε sε (Nyame kwan no) bεkyea. Na monkae εberε a na moyε kakraabi, na Ɔmaa mo dͻͻso; na monhwε sεdeε nsεmͻnedifoͻ no awieε si wieε"
  7,87,"Sε mo mu fa bi agye deε yεde somaa me no adi, ɛna εfa bi nso nnye nni a, monsi aboterε nkͻpem sε Nyankopͻn bebu yεn tεm atεn; na Ɔne atemmufoɔ mu Otemmufoͻ pa no”"